items.title: China says U.S. undermined trade talks with Huawei chip warning
items.description: China accused the United States of undermining the two countries' preliminary trade agreement reached in Geneva, Switzerland.

items.title: Former President Joe Biden diagnosed with 'aggressive' form of prostate cancer
items.description: The cancer has metastasized to the bone, according to the former president's personal office.

items.title: Trump to press Putin to end 'bloodbath' in Ukraine
items.description: U.S. President Donald Trump will speak separately with Vladimir Putin and Volodymyr Zelenskyy in hopes of ending the "bloodbath" in Ukraine.

items.title: Polish centrist's narrow presidential lead leaves pro-EU path in balance
items.description: Polish liberals performed worse than expected in a presidential election on Sunday, an exit poll showed.
